    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M-differential. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with no bushing play, and the braking system exhibits zero fade. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with 'good' condition, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight and responsive. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with sorted mechanicals.",
