    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-performing car that has been maintained with a meticulous eye. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic gloss that still turns heads; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the driver-side door handle, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free. The upholstery shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's seat, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All interior technology\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio\u2014is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, a testament to its regular service history. We recently performed a full fluid flush and replaced the brake pads, so it is mechanically prepared for many miles ahead. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the car tracks perfectly straight on the highway. This is a turn-key vehicle that bridges the gap between a showroom piece and a reliable daily companion.",
